author: jefft
msg: Add a 'dist.lite' target. This builds a minimal distribution, with these
- Smaller than real distribution (only jar + tests + javadocs) and faster
- Follows the same internal directory and filename structure as a proper
This is so that other components have a stable-ish location to point to for
jars. That need it not currently met by build/lib, or by the result of 'dist'.
